    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It's a conversion error in the JSON RPC.\n\n@tgerring When giving values greater than 2^64 (very likely) the int in `numString` will overflow. The same goes for:\n- gas\n- gasPrice\n- value\n\nThe problem is in `eth_transact` and `eth_call` using `NewTxArgs`. `big.Int` is very good at parsing numbers and you really don't need to do any conversion yourself if you'd just accept `string` only.\n",
